{"type": "article", "id": 28097, "title": "酱料架", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-13T07:00:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120232Uw8bW2hY94dkxJmo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>挤不出酱料瓶里最后那点酱料？费了九牛二虎之力却不小心挤歪？美国设计师 Daniel Kalliontzis 为了解决这个恼人的问题，发明了这款名为 Sriracha Ninja 的酱料架。虽然名字取自 Sriracha 辣椒酱，但架子本身适用于各种不同的酱料瓶，使用起来也非常简单，只要将瓶子倒置放入即可。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/254683764/sriracha-ninja-get-right-down-to-the-last-drop\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 6 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120228N2U8dz4visPJbqeh.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.92647059\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120229tKmuBrEJ0Sl86O3W.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120229B3CJ4bjRN2Ev6k1V.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55294118\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120230q8sDF20np6kgmrKb.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55882353\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}